ade_confirmed=true, status_counts={UNFILLED:14}\n- python3 scripts/run_close_review_v1.py --date 20260320 -> risk_level=NO_DATA, tomorrow_mode=review_required\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_execution_reconcile_20260320.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_execution_reconcile_20260320.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_execution_reconcile_details_20260320.csv\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774071413310}}
{"type":"message","id":"c36d4a23","parentId":"2d222c32","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:37:02.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ACTIVE_TASK.md shows Status=done, all tasks completed. Let me check if there are any other items needing attention.\n\nLooking at the heartbeat:\n- Workspace backup - need to check if done today\n- Quant ops - today is Saturday, not a trading day, so no pre-trading check needed\n- Self-improvement - should happen in afternoon/evening\n\nThe active task is done. Let me check the quant ops checklist and self-improvement checklist to see if anything needs attention today.\n\nSince today is Saturday (non-trading day), quant ops (盘前强检) don't apply. But the daily audit/enhancement panel still runs per heartbeat.\n\n\nNow I need to verify whether the workspace backup and self-improvement tasks have already been executed today.","thinkingSignature":"2c4c8f03f4d3bca83c6f6770b3f9e0fce0b0e27a65a014a2120360119f19d57e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vhfi6r54eppg_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vhfi6r54eppg_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2526,"output":234,"cacheRead":24833,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27593,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774071413312}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5875e06","parentId":"c36d4a23","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:37:02.110Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vhfi6r54eppg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774071422108}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c905c75","parentId":"d5875e06","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:37:02.112Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vhfi6r54eppg_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774071422110}}
