| pending | When corrected on prior statements, revisit the workspace evidence before summarizing architecture; do not overwrite yesterday's documented data-source policy with a generic external template\n- LRN-20260315-014 | high | pending | When asked to learn from external examples, extract strengths and adapt them to the existing system instead of copying the architecture wholesale\n- LRN-20260315-015 | high | pending | Do not ask Zhang Ling whether to continue for procedural optimization work; continue automatically and interrupt only for important decisions\n- LRN-20260316-001 | high | pending | Asynchronous promises to continue work later must be converted into a verifiable execution chain in the same turn\n- LRN-20260316-002 | high | pending | Do not claim 'I’ll continue pushing app optimization myself' without verifiable follow-through in the stated time window\n- LRN-20260316-004 | high | pending | Do not promise '中午前修复' without device-level validation; report missed deadline directly\n- LRN-20260316-005 | high | pending | After user says 'programmatic tasks don't ask me', proactively report new artifacts without waiting to be asked\n- LRN-20260316-007 | high | pending | 在“来福投研会”群聊中必须以投研组织语境发言，不能把主会话的英语学习产品职责直接套用到该群\n- LRN-20260316-008 | high | pending | For mobile compatibility bugs, stop patching a broken vendor system path after one confirmatory retest; pivot earlier to an alternative owned path and verify required assets upfront\n- LRN-20260317-002 | high | pending | 用户明确要求所有面向她展示的内容都应是中文，不能再出现英文卡片或英文面板文案\n- LRN-20260319-001 | high | pending | 做出买入推荐时必须先接入当日盘中大盘与个股实时状态，不能事后再修正名单\n- ERR-20260308-001 | high | pending | 向用户直接回传了内部错误字符串：`403 OpenAI codex passthrough requires a non-empty instructions field`，影响沟通体验。 ClawHub registry unreachable when attempting to inspect/install camoufox-cli Heartbeat dashboard generation failed because scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py is missing in personal-a-share-research-system memory_store failed because LanceD